		<title>Professional tricks to lower property tax assessment</title>
		<link>http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/14/column-wasik-taxassessment-idUSL1E8GE8TD20120514?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=everything&amp;virtualBrandChannel=11563</link>
