		<title>Column: BRICs alone won’t build your portfolio’s foundation</title>
		<link>http://in.reuters.com/article/2012/04/30/column-wasik-idINDEE83T0E720120430?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=everything&amp;virtualBrandChannel=11709</link>
