		<title>Finding ugly ducklings in a waddling market</title>
		<link>http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/27/column-wasik-ducklings-idUSL2E8FRA8720120427?feedType=RSS&amp;feedName=everything&amp;virtualBrandChannel=11563</link>
